<ENAMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">At least 40</ENAMEX> companies are coming to the capital market to raise <ENAMEX TYPE="MONEY">$ 6 billion</ENAMEX> , an amount never thought possible in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">India</ENAMEX> .
`` When they talk mega-issues , they 're truly talking mega , '' says <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">S.A. Dave</ENAMEX> , chairman of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">the Securities and Exchange Board of India</ENAMEX> .
