But the mega-issues are raising megaquestions about the rapidly evolving <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Indian</ENAMEX> capital market .
<ENAMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">One</ENAMEX> is whether there is enough money to fund the new issues without depressing stock trading .
Moreover , in the relatively unregulated <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Indian</ENAMEX> stock markets , investors frequently do n't know what they are getting when they subscribe to an issue .
